<h2 id="handling-the-card-exception">Handling the Card Exception <a class="headerlink" href="pro-error-handling#handling-the-card-exception" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>OK, back to business: we know that when a card is declined, something in that code
will throw a <code>Stripe\Error\Card</code> exception. I'm adding a little documentation just
to indicate this:</p>
